'''Osarian First-Force''' was the military space force of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Osarian]]. In [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]], it was under the command of the [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenary]], [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Grappa (Rodian)|Grappa]], and included [[Z-95 Headhunter/Legends|Z-95 Headhunters]]. When [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] and [[Mara Jade Skywalker]] arrived to negotiate with [[Nom Anor]] before the Osarian leadership, Grappa sent six Headhunters to "escort" the ''[[Jade Sabre]]'' to Osarian. However, two out of the four Headhunters were destroyed by [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Wurth Skidder]].

